item.description:
@johno2 wrote:

rawrcrystal:

Anyone else help? like a diffrent run command or somethin…?

Running a client or server? If a client you need to use something like this

[code]TITLE Client
@echo off
cls

java -Xmx800M EGUI

pause

[/code]
